---
title: Sheet Pan Mediterranean Turkey with Chickpeas, Veggies and Lemony Yogurt
description: This one and done dinner will satisfy, without too much starch! Chickpeas, tomatoes, zucchini and olives make a nourishing medley to match tender turkey scallopini!

